      "description": "This vehicle is in good, reliable condition and has been well-maintained by its previous owner. The exterior retains a nice luster, though there are a few minor stone chips on the hood and some light surface scratches consistent with normal use. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable, with only slight wear on the driver's seat bolster and floor mats. Mechanically, the car runs smoothly, with all major systems functioning as intended and a consistent service history. It\u2019s a solid, dependable choice for someone looking for a quality vehicle that has many miles of life left.",
      "price": 34500.0,
