    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Presenting a well-maintained vehicle that perfectly balances performance and value. This car has been a reliable companion, showing only the expected signs of careful use. The exterior retains a deep shine, though a close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the hood and light surface scratches near the door handles, typical for a car of this age. Inside, you will find a clean, smoke-free cabin with upholstery that remains firm and supportive, though there is some light wear visible on the driver\u2019s seat bolster. Every electronic feature\u2014from the responsive infotainment screen to the dual-zone climate control\u2014is fully functional. Mechanically, the car is in solid shape; it has been serviced regularly, offering a smooth, quiet ride and consistent power delivery. The brakes feel firm, and the tires have plenty of life left in them. This is an excellent opportunity to own a dependable, high-quality vehicle that has been treated with respect by its previous owner.",
